http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/kozhikode/Puthiyapalam-bridge-to-be-built-soon/article13995791.ece

: Minister for Public Works V.K. Ibrahim Kunju has said that the State government has allotted a rehabilitation package of Rs 26 crore to land owners who have surrendered their property for the construction of a bridge at Puthiyapalam here. The foundation for the bridge would be laid in February. He was inaugurating the renovated Puthiyapalam- Chalappuram road on Monday.Steps have been taken to renovate the Francis Road - Mankkavu road under the Kozhikode City Road Improvement Project, the Minister said.